265
00:21:32,332 --> 00:21:34,501
<i>We have nowhere else to escape!</i>

266
00:21:34,584 --> 00:21:37,462
<i>We're going to get shot
if we step outside!</i>

267
00:21:37,546 --> 00:21:38,880
<i>So let's just stay here!</i>

268
00:21:39,464 --> 00:21:43,176
<i>Adelina's right!
Let's all stay here together!</i>

269
00:21:44,011 --> 00:21:46,138
<i>God Almighty!</i>

270
00:21:46,221 --> 00:21:49,099
<i>Please don't abandon us!</i>

271
00:21:49,182 --> 00:21:51,852
<i>Save us all!</i>

272
00:21:51,935 --> 00:21:54,354
